  "texts": [
    "It enhances AI assistants by fostering deeper analytical thinking, encouraging users to form independent opinions before seeing AI suggestions (as in the Cognitive Forcing Function approach [16]) and stimulating critical thinking through AI-generated questions (similar to [25]).",
    "Additionally, Human-AI Deliberation involves users in active discussions, improving communication and transparency with AI.",
    "This engagement helps lead to more informed and nuanced decisions.Application Value of Deliberative AI.",
    "Deliberative AI is wellsuited for critical decision-making tasks, such as investment or hiring, where decision quality outweighs the need for speed or convenience.",
    "While engaging with Deliberative AI may demand more time and effort, decision-makers appreciate its ability to support well-considered outcomes."
  ],
